  "text": "To discuss our results further, we chose a simple four-level model shown in figure 5 (a) consisting of the ground state |g , the exciton states |α and |β corresponding to the splitting in the Soret band and the two-exciton state | f which implies that |α and |β are both excited [18] (for a more elaborate modeling of similar systems, see, e.g., [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ). The depicted transition wavenumbersν x y correspond to the energy difference between the states |x and |y referring to the absorption maxima in the linear spectrum.",
